4000:〔Suwa〕“Other than that, nothing in particular. They're not even classmates.”\p;
4100:〔Ban〕“Hm.”\p;
4200:Ban brought a hand to his chin, savoring the rough texture of his stubble for a moment.\p;
4300:After which, he took out several coins from his pocket and started counting them in the dark one-by-one.\p;
4400:Suwa stared at his eccentric senior with a puzzled look on his face.\p;
4500:〔Suwa〕“Wh-What're you up to?”\p;
4600:〔Ban〕“Tch, 'course I can't find a five-yen coin when I actually need one...”\p;
4700:〔Ban〕“Suwa, you have a five-yen coin on you?”\p;
4800:〔Suwa〕“*sigh*...”\p;
