7000:〔Suwa〕“Well, yeah, I've checked out a few shows like that. Last week, there was one centered on Yuri Brightman.”\p;
7100:〔Ban〕“Yuri Bri...?”\p;
7200:〔Suwa〕“<i>Y</i><i>u</i><i>r</i><i>i</i> <i>B</i><i>r</i><i>i</i><i>g</i><i>h</i><i>t</i><i>m</i><i>a</i><i>n</i><i>.</i> He's this \c:255;psychic detective\c:0; from America.”\p;
